For both normal and curses -Curses with correct projectiles graphics and animations and timers -Quick Prayers -Quick Curses

[B][Known Bugs][/B] -Attack option in first room -Deleting certain items -All the stackable stuff -Make the runes work(Unlimited spells) -Skulling when fighting

[B][Known Bugs][/B] -None atm [B][Bugs Fixed][/B] -None Atm [/COLOR]
